  "title": "Prime Mover Driver (Class 4) - Up to $5,000",
  "description": "<p>Our esteemed client in the <strong>Logistics industry</strong> is seeking a <strong>Class 4 Driver </strong>to join their dynamic team:</p>\n<ul>\n  <li><strong>Employment Type: </strong>Permanent</li>\n  <li><strong>Position:</strong> Class 4 Driver</li>\n  <li><strong>Location:</strong> Jurong East</li>\n  <li><strong>Working Hours:</strong> 5.5 days (M-F, 8.30am to 5.30pm; Sat, 8.30am to 12.30pm)</li>\n  <li><strong>Salary Package:</strong> Gross salary up to $5,000 (Basic + Trip Incentives)</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Job Responsibilities:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Transport containers between PSA Port and customer premises, and vice versa.</li>\n  <li>Ensure all containers are surveyed through PSA E-Survey before exiting the port.</li>\n  <li>Inspect the condition of containers, including floorboards and any remaining cargo, before trucking out from customer premises.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Job Requirements:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Possess Class 4 or Class 5 driving license.</li>\n  <li>Minimum 1 year of experience in driving Prime Mover.</li>\n  <li>Familiar with PSA/JP procedures.</li>\n  <li>Familiar with of Singapore roads.</li>\n  <li>Familiarity with container yard operations is an advantage.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>Ready to apply? Here’s how:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Click the APPLY button, or</li>\n  <li>Email your resume (in MS Word or PDF format) to <a href=\"mailto:adelin@intuitrecruitment.com\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>adelin@intuitrecruitment.com</strong>.</a> Include the job title in your email subject line for prompt processing.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><em><strong>Only shortlisted candidates will be notified.</strong></em></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>By submitting your application, you consent to the collection and use of your personal data under Personal Data Protection Act (PDPA).</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Adelin Chong | EA Personnel Reg No.: R1875641</p>\n<p>Intuit Recruitment Pte Ltd | EA License No.: 25C2793</p>",
